Key Match Events: Gary Rodriguez scored the winning goal in the 92nd minute.
Alexander Djiku equalized for Ghana in the 56th minute.
Jamiro Monteiro scored the first goal for Cape Verde in the 17th minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game took place in the Stade Félix Houphouët-Boigny in Cote d’Ivoire at 9 p.m Morocco time.
